  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the safety of KW-3902IV compared to placebo and to
      determine the diuretic effect of KW-3902IV compared to placebo in patients hospitalized with
      volume overload due to CHF who are refractory to high dose diuretic therapy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
